<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Invoice {{invoiceNumber}}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; margin: 0;">INVOICE</h1>
            <p style="color: #7f8c8d; margin: 5px 0;">{{invoiceNumber}}</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Bill To:</strong></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;">{{recipientName}}</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Issued By:</strong></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;">{{issuerName}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #ecf0f1; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #3498db;">
            <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Invoice Amount:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{dueDate}}</p>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Invoice ID:</strong> {{invoiceId}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
        <p>Please find attached invoice {{invoiceNumber}} for your records.</p>
        <p>You can view and download the invoice by clicking the link below:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{invoiceUrl}}" style="background-color: #3498db; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
                View Invoice
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px;">
            If you have any questions about this invoice, please contact us.
        </p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>WorkNow Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

